---
import ArrowRight from "../assets/icons/arrow-right.svg";
import Divider from "./Divider.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-12 text-center flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap justify-center gap-4 text-xs">
        <span
            class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 font-semibold bg-white px-4 py-1 rounded stroke-gray-[#94949E] will-change-transform fade-up"
            style="animation-delay: 50ms;"
        >
            <div class="relative flex items-center">
                <span
                    class="absolute inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 opacity-75 animate-ping"
                ></span>
                <span
                    class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"
                ></span>
            </div>
            Disponible para colaborar.
        </span>
        <a
            href="https://wa.me/5538611026?text=Hola%20Miguel,%20estoy%20interesado%20en%20desarrollar%20un%20proyecto%20y%20me%20gustaría%20platicar%20contigo%20para%20conocer%20tus%20servicios%20y%20opciones."        class="inline-flex mt-6 px-5 py-3 bg-black text-white rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition"
            class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-[#4E4E4E] will-change-transform fade-up"
            style="animation-delay: 90ms;"
        >
            ¿Tienes una idea? Hablemos. <ArrowRight />
        </a>
    </div>

    <h1
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold mt-6 bg-linear-to-r from-[#2B2B2B] to-[#626262] bg-clip-text text-transparent will-change-transform fade-up-slow"
        style="animation-delay: 160ms;"
    >
        Transformando ideas en productos digitales que impulsan el crecimiento
        de tu negocio.
    </h1>

    <p
        class="mt-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed will-change-transform fade-up-slow"
        style="animation-delay: 300ms;"
    >
        Ayudo a negocios a construir una presencia digital profesional mediante
        sitios web y experiencias digitales que inspiran confianza, fortalecen
        su marca y mejoran la experiencia de sus clientes.
    </p>
    <div
        class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-between mt-4
         w-full max-w-5xl
         mx-auto bg-[#E9E9E9]
         rounded-sm px-4 md:px-10 py-4
         shadow-[0_6px_6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)]
         leading-relaxed will-change-transform fade-up-slow"
        style="animation-delay: 300ms;"
    >
        <div class="flex flex-col text-left border-l px-6 py-2">
            <span class="font-bold text-2xl">+3</span>
            <span class="font-semibold text-sm">Años de experiencia</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col text-left border-l px-6 py-2">
            <span class="font-bold text-2xl">+15</span>
            <span class="font-semibold text-sm">Proyectos completados</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col text-left border-l px-6 py-2">
            <span class="font-bold text-2xl">+7</span>
            <span class="font-semibold text-sm">Clientes apoyados</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <Divider />
</section>
